OL,3,CPeople urged to 'avoid going into the
OL,4,Csea' after wastewater leak
OL,6,FPeople are being told to avoid going
OL,7,Finto the water after a sewage leak near
OL,9,Ftold people in the area that a "small
OL,10,Funderground leak" from a nearby
OL,11,Fwastewater treatment works, and
OL,12,Fadvised people not to enter the water
OL,13,Funtil it had been tested.
OL,15,FIt had previously told customers,
OL,16,F"this is a very complex issue", and
OL,17,F"we aim to resolve the matter as soon
OL,18,Fas possible".
