OL,3,CPeople urged to 'avoid going into the
OL,4,Csea' after wastewater leak
OL,6,Fwarned locals the "the pollutant
OL,7,Fhasn't been definitely identified, but
OL,8,Fit is grey with a sewage odour".
OL,10,FApologising for the leak, Welsh Water
OL,11,Fhave sought to reassure locals.
OL,12,F"Having now assessed our tanks and
OL,13,Finfrastructure on site, we have
OL,14,Fidentified a small underground leak on
OL,15,Fone of the site's treatment tanks."
