OL,3,CPeople urged to 'avoid going into the
OL,4,Csea' after wastewater leak
OL,6,FIt continues: "This is mostly
OL,7,Fgroundwater but contains a small
OL,8,Felement of wastewater and we are now
OL,9,Fworking to contain the leak and
OL,10,Fprevent it from entering the nearby
OL,11,Fwatercourse."
OL,13,F"We are undertaking daily ecological
OL,14,Fassessments to ensure that we minimise
OL,15,Fany impact on the environment,
OL,16,Fincluding the beach at Ogmore", it
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,FJohn Clark, Duty Manager for Natural
OL,20,FResources Wales, said:
