OL,3,CPeople urged to 'avoid going into the
OL,4,Csea' after wastewater leak
OL,6,F"We're continuing our investigation of
OL,7,Fthe pollution incident on the River
OL,8,FOgmore that could be impacting water
OL,9,Fquality at the Ogmore-by-Sea
OL,10,Fdesignated bathing water.
OL,12,F"Dwr Cymru Welsh Water is
OL,13,Finvestigating a potential underground
OL,14,Fleak from one of the tanks at the
OL,15,FPenybont wastewater treatment. They've
OL,16,Falso placed pollution prevention
OL,17,Fmeasures across the affected channel
OL,18,Fadjacent to the River Ogmore to try to
OL,19,Fcontain the polluted water.
