OL,3,CPeople urged to 'avoid going into the
OL,4,Csea' after wastewater leak
OL,6,F"As the pollution could be affecting
OL,7,Fthe bathing water downstream, we've
OL,8,Fdeclared an 'abnormal situation', as
OL,9,Fdefined by the Bathing Water
OL,10,FRegulations, and Vale of Glamorgan
OL,11,FCouncil has placed signs at Ogmore-by-
OL,12,FSea beach to notify people of the
OL,13,Fpollution upstream in the river. This
OL,14,Fwill remain in place until there is no
OL,15,Flonger a pollution risk."
